Barthle Urges Single EU Budget Authority, Rheinische Post Says

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-09-28T22:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/barthle-urges-single-eu-budget-authority-rheinische-post-says.html
Norbert Barthle, budget spokesman
in Angela Merkel’s Christian Democrat Party, said that in the
face of the European Union’s debt crisis, a single authority
should be created to deal with budget issues throughout the
region, Rheinische Post Düsseldorf reported, citing Barthle.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
 jcruz6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
